data.description: Duplex in the New Lotts section of Brooklyn.  The home is in disrepair and needs a lot of work.  However each unit is quite large with an eat-in kitchen, formal dining room, living room, and office.  When remodeling, there is potential to increase the number of bedrooms by changing floor plans, or converting the living/dining room spaces.  Private backyard.  Private driveway.  Second floor has a large balcony.  Great opportunity for contractors and investors based on pricing for comparable remodeled properties in the are. Due to repairs needed, the property may need to be a cash deal or rehab loan, and will be sold "as is"
